commitResults.messageTitle: Update StorageFile to load file based on new project structure
commitResults.messageBody:
The load method will first scan each line of String for an event. It
will then construct that event. If the next line of String is a
task, it will add that task to the last constructed event. The main
assertion is that the first line in the save file always has to be
an event.
